additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: For external use only. Use only as directed. Do not use on face, near eyes or in nostrils. For sensitive skin, test a small area before larger application. Discontinue use if irritation occurs. Do not use if foil seal at the mouth of the tube is broken. Keep out of reach of children. Store below 30C. Always read the label and follow the directions for use.
